{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "To tackle the issue of inaccurate Internet retrieval results, Lazaridou et al. (2022) proposed using the TF-IDF algorithm to score the retrieval results.",
    "They used each question q verbatim as a query and issued a call to Google Search via the Google Search API.",
    "For each question, they retrieved the top 20 URLs and parsed their HTML content to extract clean text, generating a set of documents D for each question q.",
    "To prevent irrelevant information from hindering the resolution of a user's query, Hu et al. (2023) designed a gating circuit.",
    "This circuit utilised a dual-encoder dot product to calculate similarity and a gating circuit based on term weights."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "To tackle the issue of inaccurate Internet retrieval results, Lazaridou et al. (2022) proposed using the TF-IDF algorithm to score the retrieval results.",
    "To prevent irrelevant information from hindering the resolution of a user's query, Hu et al. (2023) designed a gating circuit."
  ]
}